data.title: Sakasa tsurushi shibari nawa (1985)
data.meta_description: Sakasa tsurushi shibari nawa: Directed by Shûji Kataoka. With Shirô Shimomoto, Hiromi Saotome, Yutaka Ikejima. THE LEGEND BEGINS! This prequel to the pink cult hit S&M Hunter tells the origin story of how an average salary man became the world's first S&M superhero! How did he lose his eye? Why is bad girl Meg chasing him in the first place? And why did Maria become a masochist? Long out of print and hungered for by Pink Eiga fans the world over, Pink Eiga Inc. is proud to release the only true superhero movie that matters in a flooded market of comic book adaptations!
